1.2.name: wordpress/swipehq-payment-gateway-woocommerce
1.2.description:
This is the Swipe HQ payment gateway for WooCommerce. Allows you to use Swipe HQ payment gateway with the WooCommerce plugin. It uses the redirect method, the user is redirected to swipehq so that you don't have to install an SSL certificate on your site.

Visit [http://www.swipehq.com]
